node.text:
High Reps & Medium Weight! Let’s get it 🦾

I really enjoy what I do! I Make sure to keep it fun and creative! But just because I’m smiling doesn’t mean I’m not putting in work! Keep your workouts exciting and don’t overwhelm yourself with “perfection”, It will all come! SMILE a little , dance a little more & most IMPORTANTLY.. SWEAT A LOT! 🥵

I had to rock out since those were the vibes on the gym 🎸 💥 😝

SWIPE ✔️ SAVE ✔️ TRY ✔️ SHARE

node.text: With the one and ONLY @simonourianmd1 👨‍⚕️! I’ve gotten questions about skin, stretch marks , and just smoothness overall! From being into fitness I’ve seen stretch marks from head to toe! Under arm pits, inner thighs , Glutes , tummy etc! It can be genetic but mainly from your body changing drastically in size, losing weight gaining weight , gaining muscles , growing in size from having babies etc! Thank you @simonourianmd1 for taking care of my skin! I know stretch marks aren’t necessarily a “bad thing” but for those who may want to get rid of them or are a little timid or insecure about hiding them please contact Epion for more details! You won’t regret it! Painless treatments and more!

node.text:
There’s something about the energy in the gym that makes a lot of people feel Anxious , Defeated , Intimidated or maybe even incapable.. but we all have that rush, that feeling. It’s a serious thing to Challenge your body, to do things it doesn’t normally do. The energy is very high, very intense, we are all pushing limits that maybe some of us never thought we had. We are all dealing with defeat at times. We’re working on getting better, which is one of the Hardest things to do. Great things don’t come easy. We all struggle with soreness, we all struggle with Staying Motivated and Consistent. Our bodies are changing, it’s constantly trying to adjust & along the way .. our Mental is also being Challenged, taking us to a whole nother level. You’re not alone, keep pushing, CAUSE WE ALL ARE. Do it for you & train yourself to be so Mentally Strong that nothing can shake you. If it does, persevere , Rise Above it. You cannot be defeated. Tell yourself , talk to yourself , Encourage “Self” and believe it. Confidence is 🔑 !

@1stphorm
